   <refbody>
      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <indexterm class="- topic/indexterm ">controller box</indexterm>
      </section>
      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">
            <fig class="- topic/fig ">
               <image href="../Images/25_kva_nam_power_block_principle_diagram_85mm_0000147362.svg"
                      scalefit="yes"
                      scope="local"
                      translate="yes"
                      xml:lang="en"
                      placement="inline"
                      class="- topic/image "/>
            </fig>
         </p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">The controller box controls the entire UPS system and
consists of 2 PCBs:<ul class="- topic/ul ">
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Controller board</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Adapter board</p>
               </li>
            </ul>
         </p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">The controller box has the following functions:<ul class="- topic/ul ">
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">controls the power modules</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">communicates with the Smart Slot Module (NMC, Modbus)</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">communicates with the HMI</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">communicates with the interface board</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">communicates with the external connection board via the interface
board</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">communicates with the static bypass switch controller</p>
               </li>
            </ul>
         </p>
      </section>
